    "detail": "My husband and I had an amazing stay at Radisson Blue Uluwatu, everything was perfect. Our room was very spacious with the most comfortable bed I have ever slept on while on holiday. We had a ground floor room with our very lawned area overlooking the pool with some day beds that were lovely to relax on in the afternoon while having a few drinks. The pool was amazing and so was the service we received from all the staff. We stayed for 4 nights and had every single meal here and none of them disappointed. It was all very well priced too. We will definitely be coming back here every time we visit Bali.",
